Description: *****
        tayne
        *****
        
        Companion to entr_.
        
        .. _entr: http://entrproject.org/
        
        =====
        Usage
        =====
        
        Create a configuration file in the same directory called ``.taynerc``::
        
            [tayne]
            patterns =
                **/*.py
                **/*.ini
            command = py.test tayne.py && pycodestyle tayne.py
        
        Then invoke as follows::
        
            tayne
        
        Or::
        
            tayne | entr
        
